<h1>Your Text Analysis</h1>

<h2>Number of Words: <%= @analyzed_text.split(" ").length %></h2>

<h2>Vowels: <%= @analyzed_text.scan(/[aeiou]/).count %></h2>

<h2>Consonants: <%= @analyzed_text.scan(/[bcdfghjklmnpqrstvxyz]/).count %></h2>

<h2>Most Common Letter: <%= @letter.upcase %>, used <%= @freq %> times</h2>
